Show HN: New Year Card Design Templates and Editor
text:
Hello everyone. We've been working on this for a couple of weeks and wanted to share these amazing free to use New Year Card template designs (https://www.creatosaurus.io/apps/muse/templates/cards/new-ye...).

Cheers to 2023! Ring in the new year by creating custom-made happy new poster greetings with our graphic design tool - Muse.

Is there a design layout you have in mind for your happy new year card poster card? Let that creative zeal come to life with Muse — Pro graphic design editor. Have no idea where to start? Muse has got you covered with a ton of free new year wishes templates and overall 1000+ free design templates.

Here’s what up for grabs

- A vast collection of high-quality new year card templates - Seamless personalisation - Zero-hassle editing tools - Create from scratch or use pre-existing templates - Easily downloadable templates - Seamless save your favourite new year card creation - Professional happy new year poster templates for all - Instant sharing and printing feature

I'm here to answer all your questions and collect feedback!

We also launched this on the Product Hunt(https://www.producthunt.com/posts/new-year-card-templates), do share your feedbacks and insights.
